# ENCODE4 Integrated Regulation Track

track encode4Reg
superTrack on show
shortLabel ENCODE4 Regulation
longLabel Integrated Regulation from ENCODE 4
group regulation
priority 0.5
pennantIcon New red ../goldenPath/newsarch.html#TBD "Released TBD"
html encode4Reg.html

    track encode4RegMarkH3k27ac
